Heat Defeat Celtics 102-91 to Lead NBA Second-Round Playoff Series 2-0

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-05-04T01:37:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/heat-defeat-celtics-102-91-to-lead-nba-second-round-playoff-series-2-0.html
The  Miami Heat  beat the  Boston  Celtics
102-91 to lead their National Basketball Association second-
round playoff series by two games to none.  The teams head to Boston for the next two games in the
best-of-seven Eastern Conference series, with Game 3 scheduled
for May 7.  Also tonight, The Memphis Grizzlies will try to take a 2-0
lead in games against the Oklahoma City Thunder in their Western
Conference series.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  